cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.CY, cs.DS, cs.IT 

The paper deals with privacy preservation and data gathering in smart grids, which involves security and system aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves control and optimization of the smart grid, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper involves statistical analysis and data processing, which can be categorized under cs.CY (Computational Geometry). The paper also involves simulation results, which can be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
